---
title: Turkey and Veggies Tacos 'Al Pastor' with Pineapple Salsa
description: If ever there was a fusion food, tacos al pastor would be it. Although it looms large in the canon of Mexican food, the original recipe was inspired by Lebanese immigrants, who adapted it from shawarma. It typically features pork, but we're making it with turkey tonight!
